                                                    <fixVersion>Lustre 2.10.0</fixVersion>
                                        <due></due>
                            <votes>0</votes>
                                    <watches>5</watches>
                                                                            <comments>
                            <comment id="197057" author="jhammond" created="Thu, 25 May 2017 14:39:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Note that &lt;tt&gt;mdt_add_dirty_flag()&lt;/tt&gt; is called from the close path. As explained in &lt;tt&gt;mdc_close()&lt;/tt&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;        /* To avoid a livelock (bug 7034), we need to send CLOSE RPCs to a                
         * portal whose threads are not taking any DLM locks and are therefore            
         * always progressing */
        req-&amp;gt;rq_request_portal = MDS_READPAGE_PORTAL;
        ptlrpc_at_set_req_timeout(req);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;And so this is another instance of &lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=7034&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=7034&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="195046" author="pjones" created="Tue, 9 May 2017 04:19:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Landed for 2.10&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="195026" author="gerrit" created="Tue, 9 May 2017 03:47:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Oleg Drokin (oleg.drokin@intel.com) merged in patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/26870/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/26870/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Subject: &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9385&quot; title=&quot;mdt_add_dirty_flag() should not use MDS_INODELOCK_XATTR&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-9385&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-9385&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; mdt: remove XATTR locking from mdt_add_dirty_flag()&lt;br/&gt;
